a little month ago, I  tried to convince Petra and You, to continue the evening by dancing the stars away after one of those cozy dinners.
looking over your glasses, as you always did, you declined full of laughter and sent us into the night.
that laughter, your immense generosity making me feel as a part of your family, your ever brilliant talent, will remain with me always and ever my dear Peter.
